&gt; 
&gt; 
 Her crimson optics spotted the newcomer. It took her a moment to register 
who it was. The memories were finally returning to her. 

&quot;Ahh.. Perceptor.&quot; Pausing a moment. &quot;Hydras has been contacting me? I... My 
internal com must be totally down.&quot; 

She smirked, &quot;I have found a new haven, Perceptor. But, if Hydras needs me, I 
shall return immediately.&quot; She turned to Scourge. &quot;Dare you wish to come with 
me my dear friend?&quot; There was more of a bond now & liking to Scourge. She 
dare not leave him or abandon him.... not like she had been in the past. 

Then turned to Azureblade. &quot;The same courtesy extends to you, my friend.&quot;  

